cements were less favorable than those who cracked the starting lineup. We must be mindful of the weather risk for **Chase Meidroth** and **Junior Caminero**, both facing a 39% rain probability, and that several players, including **Dillon Dingler** and **Logan O'Hoppe**, still have their exact lineup positions pending.",
